data.description: This custom built home located on fairway number 11 at the Macomb Country Club offers 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths, 2 half baths and a total of 5,800 square feet of living space. The main level of the home is finished with a two story foyer with an open stairway, formal dining and living rooms, a large family room that is open to the stylish kitchen with a large center island, a sliding glass door to a deck area and great views of woods and golf course. The upper level has four bedrooms, one is the master suite with a gas fireplace, large suite bath and a walk-in closet. Just steps away is the laundry room, very conveniently located. The lower level has tall ceilings, and has a walkout to the back yard, large game room with wet bar, media room, home gym and play room, all finished with tile flooring. In the basement, you will also find a guest bedroom and bath. This home has other great features as well as an attached three car garage.
